<h3 id="toc2"><span>ATTENTION: ALL CENTRE PUGILISTS</span></h3>
<div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F8FF;"></div>
<p>Bobble the Clown Shark is in <strong><span style="color: #164F7F; font-size: 110%;"><em>COWABUNGA, DUDE!!!</em></span>-Level Danger</strong>.</p>
<p>We need <em>YOUR</em> help to get him back from the Deviant menace. To do this, we need a hardened fighter with FISTS OF STEEL. To prove your worth, all you need to do is 100 push-ups, 100 sit-ups, and 100 squats, and drink a peanut butter &amp; banana chocolate protein shake. But you gotta be quick so that Bobble can get back on the air and teach these kids karate!</p>
<p>Once you have read this document, please report to your Fitness Centre. Long Island Iced Tea will be administered when you get there. HURRY!</p>
</div>
