<p>Watch <strong>SUPER-PUGILIST Clark &quot;PUNCH-DOCTOR&quot; Savage, Jr.</strong>, in an EPIC once-in-a-lifetime UNLICENSED match-up <em>VS.</em> <strong>SELACHIAN Richard C. Chappell</strong>. Tune in on March 12th at 8/7 Central to witness ol' Doc Savage pulverize that Selachian wretch.</p>
<p>That's right, watch Centre SmackDown-993, LIVE, at the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Dr. Mike Tyson Colosseum</span>. Buy your tickets TODAY!</p>
